								</condition>
							</supportDesc>
							<layoutDesc>
								<layout columns="1" writtenLines="4">
									<p>First and final lines indented although perhaps an attempt to center text for each line.</p>
								</layout>
							</layoutDesc>
						</objectDesc>
						<handDesc ana="#impressed.inscribed.chiseled">
							<handNote>Lettering is inconsistent in form, with some letters cramped as though the inscriber ran out of space. In particular, the first and last characters of line 2, an 'L' and an 'I' are not equidistant to the border, suggesting that the lettering was inscribed after the border. Note also the uneven spacing of the word 'Manibus' on line 1.
							</handNote>
						</handDesc>
						<decoDesc>
							<decoNote ana="#blank">
								<p>Undulating border incised around text. Sunken triangles at corners create tabula ansata motif.</p>
							</decoNote>
						</decoDesc>
			</physDesc>
